OL,6,FA priest is set to face 34 sexual
OL,7,Fabuse charges against members of his
OL,8,Fcongregation.
OL,10,FThe Rev Christopher Brain led an
OL,11,FEvangelical movement called the Nine
OL,12,FO'Clock Service in between 1986 and
OL,13,F1995.
OL,15,FThe charges relate to allegations of
OL,16,Fsexual offences committed against 11
OL,17,Fwomen who had joined the movement.
