OL,4,Cabuse charges
OL,6,FBrain, now 66, is facing one count of
OL,7,Frape and 33 counts of indecent
OL,8,Fassault, alleged to have been
OL,9,Fcommitted between 1981 and 1995.
OL,11,FHe has been summonsed to attend
OL,12,FSheffield Magistrates' Court on 18
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FThe Nine O'Clock Service was initially
OL,16,Fheld at St Thomas' Church in Crookes,
OL,17,Fbefore later moving to Ponds Forge in
OL,18,Fthe city centre.
