OL,8,Fcomplex and wide-ranging investigation
OL,9,Finto events dating back 30 or more
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F"The police investigation was launched
OL,13,Fin 2020, when a number of victims came
OL,14,Fforward to report the allegations to
OL,15,Fus. Since this time, an investigation
OL,16,Fteam has been working hard to build up
OL,17,Fa full picture of what is reported to
OL,18,Fhave happened."
